Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:55.64,Default-CN,,0,0,0,,喂 那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.69,Default-CN,,0,0,0,,应该是队伍全灭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.39,Default-CN,,0,0,0,,真惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.04,Default-CN,,0,0,0,,只有自己一个人活了下来…
